abstract: Apple rarely makes sweeping changes to its product line, which is why its new MacBook Pro laptops look identical to older models.
snippet: Apple rarely makes sweeping changes to its product line, which is why its new MacBook Pro laptops look identical to older models.
lead_paragraph: Apple rarely makes sweeping changes to its product line, which is why its new MacBook Pro laptops look identical to older models. Only the innards are different, offering improved wireless networking and processing speed.

headline.main: MacBook Pros Look Like Older Models, but the Innards Are Different
headline.print_headline: MacBook Pros Look Like Older Models, but the Innards Are Different
